framework.logging

Interface Logger

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FeedbackJsonLogger, FeedbackTextSummaryLogger, LocalJsonLogger, LocalTextSummaryLogger

    public interface Logger
    This interface defines how grade loggers should behave.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • save

        void save(String projectName,
        String userId,
        List<CheckResult> featureResults,
        List<CheckResult> restrictionResults,
        String comments,
        double gradePercentage)
        Each implementing class will define this method, which saves or logs the data to a destination.
        Parameters:
        projectName - The name of the current project
        userId - The ID of the user grade that is being logged
        featureResults - The results from grading the features
        restrictionResults - The results from grading the restrictions
        comments - Additional comments. May be empty
